{"tid":1971770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣今日零確診","createTime":"2020-04-14T06:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T11:44:51.000Z","uid":181720,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"412e4b1ebd55be7160bb825069d28d624fb5f502","tid":1971770,"uid":181720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"<ins>一個月來台灣首次零確診 陳時中：疫情還沒過，但值得稍微高興一下</ins><br />\n<br />\n中央流行疫情指揮中心今（14）日表示，國內今日無新增確診病例，指揮中心指揮官陳時中指出，這是距離上次零確診（3月8日、3月9日）以來，在36日連續每日都有新增確診案例後，第一次再出現零確診的情況。陳時中表示，疫情還沒過，但值得大家稍微高興一下。<br />\n<br />\n國內目前累計案例為393例確診，分別為338例境外移入及55例本土病例。確診個案中6人死亡，124人解除隔離，其餘持續住院隔離中。有關3月30日返台專案航班共214名湖北返台民眾，已於今日解除隔離，並返家進行14天自主健康管理。<br />\n<br />\n核稿編輯：楊士範"},{"pid":"8b25ebe2c4fe6c4f50f6ba554fabd3fcfc999668","tid":1971770,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1e087baa669c65ba3a8c977dc355c3bfeb0a0c","tid":1971770,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"蕭生又中神呀"},{"pid":"1a8438db90d893a7ecca2242a55703c049397aac","tid":1971770,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb5d70c90c3b0f946f7b9d5eb702f796eeb7058","tid":1971770,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"俾我飛台灣未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3400ad0188589778de81af7c3025a1b991f7a3b7","tid":1971770,"uid":51369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"旅行去台灣最安全"},{"pid":"20c49b6ae54f4bd62f07913df3ea32050b22c0d3","tid":1971770,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"今日解除隔離，並返家進行14天自主健康